with lived experience whom we engage through training, psychosocial support, and socio-economic empowerment to be mental health ambassadors within their communities.\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b27ee4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2b27ee4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bad0f8 elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3bad0f8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:300,&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2023\" height=\"1772\" src=\"https:\/\/mental360.or.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Rafiki-Transparent-6.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1071\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mental360.or.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Rafiki-Transparent-6.webp 2023w, https:\/\/mental360.or.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Rafiki-Transparent-6-600x526.webp 600w, https:\/\/mental360.or.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Rafiki-Transparent-6-300x263.webp 300w, https:\/\/mental360.or.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Rafiki-Transparent-6-1024x897.webp 1024w, https:\/\/mental360.or.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Rafiki-Transparent-6-768x673.webp 768w, https:\/\/mental360.or.ke\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Rafiki-Transparent-6-1536x1345.webp 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2023px) 100vw, 2023px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-42bf19d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"42bf19d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f89ef1 e-con-full animated-slow e-flex elementor-invisible e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5f89ef1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInLeft&quot;,&quot;animation_delay&quot;:100,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2346b7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a2346b7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-95d3942 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"95d3942\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInDown&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:200,&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why The Rafikis<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4275c5e animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4275c5e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:200,&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To become a Rafiki, individuals undergo comprehensive training in the Rafiki Model, equipping them with fundamental mental health concepts and practical support techniques. Rafikis are community peer mental health champions who provide invaluable support, fostering resilience and well-being among their peers.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee3be5c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ee3be5c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-14bf776 e-con-full animated-slow e-flex elementor-invisible e-con e-child\" data-id=\"14bf776\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInRight&quot;,&quot;animation_delay&quot;:100,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-62761f3 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"62761f3\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d675c9 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3d675c9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInDown&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:200,&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Rafikis Matter<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-72904c6 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"72904c6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:200,&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Kenya faces a critical shortage of mental health professionals, with only <a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.who.int\/media\/docs\/default-source\/mental-health\/mental-health-atlas-2020-country-profiles\/ken.pdf?sfvrsn=b0481dcf_7&amp;download=true\">116 psychiatrists <\/a>serving a population of 50 million. This severe imbalance creates an urgent need for alternative models of mental health support.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd223b7 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cd223b7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInDown&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:200,&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Vision For The Future<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c93ca89 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c93ca89\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:200,&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Our vision is ambitious: we foresee a future where every Kenyan has access to a Rafiki. By decentralizing mental health education and support, we aim to create a society where mental health challenges are met with understanding, compassion, and effective intervention at the grassroots.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"